# Keep the docker build context small. We DO need packages/ and plugins/ source
# (the image is built multi-stage inside Docker), so unlike the create-app
# default we do not exclude them — only build outputs, deps, and local files.
.git
.yarn/cache
.yarn/install-state.gz
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/dist-types
dist-types
*.local.yaml
e2e-test-report
coverage
RESUME.md
